name: Nite Ize DoohicKey Key Tool
description: The Doohickey won’t replace a trusty pocket knife, but it will free a beer from the bottle.Made of stainless steel.Sized for a key chain or strap.Includes box cutter, bottle opener, wrench, ruler, Phillips and flat head screw drivers and a nail/staple remover.TSA friendly.Size is 67 x 18 x 6mm.
